  <refnamediv>
    <refname>correl_spherical</refname>
    <refpurpose> a template function to model spherical correlation </refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>res = correl_spherical(x,p)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  
  <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>x</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>a value of distance for which we want to compute the correlation.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>p</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>a vector of parameters for the template correlation model.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>res</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>value of the correlation.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>This function is used during the learning of kriging models and it's also used for the computation of estimations.</para>
  </refsection>
  
